TI  - Factors influencing Shaanxi and Gansu farmers' willingness to purchase weather insurance
T2  - CHINA AGRICULTURAL ECONOMIC REVIEW
LA  - English
CP  - International Conference on Agricultural Risk and Food Security (ARFS)
KW  - China
