TI  - Consumer Awareness, Utilization, and Acceptance of Orange-Fleshed Sweet Potato (Ipomoea Batatas (L.) Lam) Value-Added Food Products in Elgeyo Marakwet County, Kenya
T2  - CURRENT RESEARCH IN NUTRITION AND FOOD SCIENCE
