KW  - risk preference aggregation and disaggregation
KW  - risk preference elicitation
KW  - rural Ethiopia
KW  - SAFETY NET PROGRAM
KW  - ATTITUDES
KW  - BEHAVIOR
KW  - AVERSION
KW  - DEMAND
