TI  - Unlocking farmers' potential: the impact of ICT on farmers' TFP in grain production
T2  - CHINA AGRICULTURAL ECONOMIC REVIEW
LA  - English
KW  - Information and communication technology (ICT)
KW  - Information software usage
KW  - Farmers
KW  - Grain total factor productivity (TFP)
KW  - INFORMATION
KW  - TECHNOLOGY
