TI  - Incorporating indigenous knowledge systems-based climate services in anticipatory action in Zimbabwe: an ex-ante assessment
T2  - FRONTIERS IN CLIMATE
LA  - English
KW  - anticipatory action
KW  - indigenous knowledge systems
