TI  - Invasion, Distribution, Monitoring and Farmers Perception of Fall Armyworm (Spodoptera frugiperda) and Farm-Level Management Practices in Bangladesh
T2  - INSECTS
LA  - English
KW  - fall armyworm
KW  - transboundary pest
KW  - invasive species
KW  - farmers perception
KW  - integrated pest management
KW  - economic analysis of pesticide use
KW  - LEPIDOPTERA-NOCTUIDAE
KW  - HOST STRAINS
KW  - JE SMITH
