TI  - Aiming at low nitrogen leaching diets based on nitrogen fertilizer regulatory policy: A regional bio-economic assessment of the Zayandeh-Rud river basin-Iran
T2  - JOURNAL OF ENVIRONMENTAL MANAGEMENT
