TI  - Unsupervised segmentation and clustering time series approach to Southern Africa rainfall regime changes
T2  - GEOSCIENCE DATA JOURNAL
LA  - English
KW  - ARIMA
KW  - coastal
KW  - Facebook Prophet
KW  - hidden Markov model regression
KW  - regression with hidden logistic process
