TI  - TOO LITTLE TOO LATE: WELFARE IMPACTS OF RAINFALL SHOCKS IN RURAL INDONESIA
T2  - BULLETIN OF INDONESIAN ECONOMIC STUDIES
LA  - English
KW  - welfare
KW  - rainfall shocks
KW  - social protection
KW  - agriculture
KW  - rice
