TI  - QTLs associated with root traits increase yield in upland rice when transferred through marker-assisted selection
T2  - THEORETICAL AND APPLIED GENETICS
LA  - English
KW  - NEAR-ISOGENIC-LINES
KW  - DROUGHT-RESISTANCE
