TI  - Doubled-up legume rotations improve soil fertility and maintain productivity under variable conditions in maize-based cropping systems in Malawi
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - APSIM
KW  - Soil fertility
KW  - Climate variability
KW  - Legume rotation
