TI  - Agricultural development promises more growth and less poverty in Africa: Modelling the potential impact of implementing the Comprehensive Africa Agriculture Development Programme in six countries
T2  - DEVELOPMENT POLICY REVIEW
LA  - English
KW  - Africa
KW  - agricultural development
