TI  - Conservation agriculture based sustainable intensification: Increasing yields and water productivity for smallholders of the Eastern Gangetic Plains
T2  - FIELD CROPS RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Cropping systems
KW  - Tillage
KW  - Farmers' participatory trials
KW  - Rice-maize
