TI  - Higher sowing density of pearl millet increases productivity and water use efficiency in high evaporative demand seasons
T2  - FRONTIERS IN PLANT SCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - climate change
KW  - sustainable intensification
KW  - canopy architecture
KW  - semi-arid tropics
