TI  - Impact of COVID-19 on aquaculture and fisheries in ASEAN countries: some aspects of challenges, mitigations for future strategies in Malaysia
T2  - DESALINATION AND WATER TREATMENT
LA  - English
KW  - COVID-19 Pandemic
KW  - Aquaculture
KW  - Fisheries
