TI  - Spatiotemporal analysis of drought in the Sahelian region of northeastern Nigeria, sub-Saharan Africa
T2  - THEORETICAL AND APPLIED CLIMATOLOGY
LA  - English
KW  - Drought monitoring
KW  - MODIS
KW  - Sahelian region
KW  - Vegetation indices
