TI  - Wheat yield gaps and its implications on food security in East Africa: a comprehensive analysis of factors and consequences
T2  - COGENT FOOD & AGRICULTURE
LA  - English
KW  - East Africa
KW  - food security
KW  - income
KW  - technology adoption
KW  - wheat yield gap
